Freshly hatched bee Maya is a little whirlwind and won't follow the rules
of the hive. One of these rules is not to trust the hornets that live
beyond the meadow. When the Royal Jelly is stolen, the hornets are suspected
and Maya is thought to be their accomplice. No one believes that she is the
innocent victim and no one will stand by her except for her good-natured and
best friend Willy. After a long and eventful journey to the hornets hive
Maya and Willy soon discover the true culprit and the two friends finally
bond with the other residents of the opulent meadow.
